# UIControlSystem

## Purpose
Applies all pending one-frame mutation commands to persistent UI data components each frame.
Processes layout-load requests (parses JSON files and creates entity trees) and subtree-destroy
requests (recursively defers entity destruction). Guards on ResourceMapSingletonComponent presence;
if absent, returns immediately without processing anything.

## Input Components
| Component | Access |
|---|---|
| ResourceMapSingletonComponent | read |
| BaseComponent | read / write |
| ImageComponent | read / write |
| TextComponent | read / write |
| UIUpdateTransformOneFrameComponent | read / write |
| UIUpdateParentOneFrameComponent | read / write |
| UIUpdateEnableOneFrameComponent | read / write |
| UIUpdateUUIDOneFrameComponent | read / write |
| UIUpdateImageUUIDOneFrameComponent | read / write |
| UIUpdateTextOneFrameComponent | read / write |
| LoadLayoutEvent | read |
| UIDestroyOneFrameComponent | read |

## Output Components
| Component | Access | Notes |
|---|---|---|
| BaseComponent | write / add (deferred) | Modified in-place by mutation commands; created in bulk when loading JSON layouts |
| ImageComponent | write / add (deferred) | Modified in-place; created when a JSON node has a ui.image entry |
| TextComponent | write / add (deferred) | Modified in-place; created when a JSON node has a ui.text entry |
| LayoutContainerComponent | add (deferred) | Created when a JSON node declares a layout (vertical/horizontal stack or grid) |
| UIClipComponent | add (deferred) | Created when a JSON node declares a clip (scissor-masked sub-tree + scroll offset) |
